Sources de rayons : 4, 8, 16, 32, 64 mm


Forward projections sur 120 projs avec PVE (sigma0pve_default = 0.9008418065898374; alphapve_default = 0.025745123547513887) donc FWHM au centre = 13mm

python forwardprojection.py -i illustration_pve/source_16.mha -o illustration_pve/ -g data/geom_120.xml -a data/acf_ct_air.mhd --pve --output_ref projs_16;
python forwardprojection.py -i illustration_pve/source_32.mha -o illustration_pve/ -g data/geom_120.xml -a data/acf_ct_air.mhd --pve --output_ref projs_32;
python forwardprojection.py -i illustration_pve/source_64.mha -o illustration_pve/ -g data/geom_120.xml -a data/acf_ct_air.mhd --pve --output_ref projs_64

Reconstructions

python osem_reconstruction.py -i illustration_pve/projs_4_PVE.mha -o illustration_pve/recons_4.mha --like illustration_pve/source_4.mha --data_folder data --beta 0 --nprojpersubset 10 -n 10 --FB Zeng
python osem_reconstruction.py -i illustration_pve/projs_8_PVE.mha -o illustration_pve/recons_8.mha --like illustration_pve/source_4.mha --data_folder data --beta 0 --nprojpersubset 10 -n 10 --FB Zeng
python osem_reconstruction.py -i illustration_pve/projs_16_PVE.mha -o illustration_pve/recons_16.mha --like illustration_pve/source_4.mha --data_folder data --beta 0 --nprojpersubset 10 -n 10 --FB Zeng
python osem_reconstruction.py -i illustration_pve/projs_32_PVE.mha -o illustration_pve/recons_32.mha --like illustration_pve/source_4.mha --data_folder data --beta 0 --nprojpersubset 10 -n 10 --FB Zeng

python osem_reconstruction.py -i illustration_pve/projs_64_PVE.mha -o illustration_pve/recons_64.mha --like illustration_pve/source_4.mha --data_folder data --beta 0 --nprojpersubset 10 -n 10 --FB Zeng
